<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><strong class="selflink">Gordon Brown</strong></b> (<a href="/wiki/Labour_Party_(UK)" title="Labour Party (UK)">Labour</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><a href="/wiki/David_Cameron" title="David Cameron">David Cameron</a></b> (<a href="/wiki/Conservative_Party_(UK)" title="Conservative Party (UK)">Conservatives</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><b><a href="/wiki/Nick_Clegg" title="Nick Clegg">Nick Clegg</a></b> (<a href="/wiki/Liberal_Democrats" title="Liberal Democrats">Liberal Democrats</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Peter_Robinson_(politician)" title="Peter Robinson (politician)">Peter Robinson</a> (<a href="/wiki/Democratic_Unionist_Party" title="Democratic Unionist Party">DUP</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alex_Salmond" title="Alex Salmond">Alex Salmond</a> (<a href="/wiki/Scottish_National_Party" title="Scottish National Party">SNP</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Gerry_Adams" title="Gerry Adams">Gerry Adams</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sinn_F%C3%A9in" title="Sinn Féin">Sinn Féin</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ieuan_Wyn_Jones" title="Ieuan Wyn Jones">Ieuan Wyn Jones</a> (<a href="/wiki/Plaid_Cymru" title="Plaid Cymru">Plaid Cymru</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mark_Durkan" title="Mark Durkan">Mark Durkan</a> (<a href="/wiki/Social_Democratic_and_Labour_Party" title="Social Democratic and Labour Party">SDLP</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Taylor_(UK_politician)" title="Richard Taylor (UK politician)">Richard Taylor</a> (<a href="/wiki/Health_Concern" title="Health Concern" class="mw-redirect">Health Concern</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Linda_Smith_(UK_politician)&