<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><i>President: <a href="/wiki/Mirek_Topol%C3%A1nek" title="Mirek Topolánek">Topolánek</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_the_Czech_Republic" title="List of Prime Ministers of the Czech Republic">CZ</a>)</i><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Werner_Faymann" title="Werner Faymann">Faymann</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Chancellor_of_Austria" title="Chancellor of Austria">AT</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Herman_Van_Rompuy" title="Herman Van Rompuy">Van Rompuy</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Belgium" title="List of Prime Ministers of Belgium">BE</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sergey_Stanishev" title="Sergey Stanishev" class="mw-redirect">Stanishev</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Bulgaria" title="List of Prime Ministers of Bulgaria">BG</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Dimitris_Christofias" title="Dimitris Christofias">Christofias</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/President_of_Cyprus" title="President of Cyprus">CY</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Angela_Merkel" title="Angela Merkel">Merkel</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Chancellor_of_Germany_(Federal_Republic)" title="Chancellor of Germany (Federal Republic)">DE</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anders_Fogh_Rasmussen" title="Anders Fogh Rasmussen">Rasmussen</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Denmark" title="Prime Minister of Denmark">DK</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Andrus_Ansip" title="Andrus Ansip">Ansip</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Estonia" title="Prime Minister of Estonia">ET</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Matti_Vanhanen" title="Matti Vanhanen">Vanhanen</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Finland" title="Prime Minister of Finland">FI</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Nicolas_Sarkozy" title="Nicolas Sarkozy">Sarkozy</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/President_of_France" title="President of France">FR</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kostas_Karamanlis" title="Kostas Karamanlis">Karamanlis</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Greece" title="Prime Minister of Greece">GR</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ferenc_Gyurcs%C3%A1ny" title="Ferenc Gyurcsány">Gyurcsány</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Hungary" title="List of Prime Ministers of Hungary">HU</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Brian_Cowen" title="Brian Cowen">Cowen</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Taoiseach" title="Taoiseach">IE</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Silvio_Berlusconi" title="Silvio Berlusconi">Berlusconi</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Italy" title="Prime Minister of Italy">IT</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Valdis_Dombrovskis" title="Valdis Dombrovskis">Dombrovskis</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Latvia" title="Prime Minister of Latvia">LV</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Andrius_Kubilius" title="Andrius Kubilius">Kubilius</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_rulers_of_Lithuania" title="List of rulers of Lithuania">LT</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jean-Claude_Juncker" title="Jean-Claude Juncker">Juncker</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Luxembourg" title="List of Prime Ministers of Luxembourg">LU</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lawrence_Gonzi" title="Lawrence Gonzi">Gonzi</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Malta" title="Prime Minister of Malta">MT</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jan_Peter_Balkenende" title="Jan Peter Balkenende">Balkenende</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_the_Netherlands" title="Prime Minister of the Netherlands">NL</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Donald_Tusk" title="Donald Tusk">Tusk</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_the_Republic_of_Poland" title="Prime Minister of the Republic of Poland">PL</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jos%C3%A9_S%C3%B3crates" title="José Sócrates">Sócrates</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Portugal" title="List of Prime Ministers of Portugal">PT</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Emil_Boc" title="Emil Boc">Boc</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Romania" title="Prime Minister of Romania">RO</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Robert_Fico" title="Robert Fico">Fico</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/List_of_Prime_Ministers_of_Slovakia" title="List of Prime Ministers of Slovakia">SK</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Borut_Pahor" title="Borut Pahor">Pahor</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Slovenia" title="Prime Minister of Slovenia">SI</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jos%C3%A9_Luis_Rodr%C3%ADguez_Zapatero" title="José Luis Rodríguez Zapatero">Zapatero</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Spain" title="Prime Minister of Spain">ES</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fredrik_Reinfeldt" title="Fredrik Reinfeldt">Reinfeldt</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Sweden" title="Prime Minister of Sweden">SE</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">Brown</strong>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_the_United_Kingdom" title="Prime Minister of the United Kingdom">UK</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jos%C3%A9_Manuel_Barroso" title="José Manuel Barroso">Barroso</a>&#160;(<a href="/wiki/President_of_the_European_Commission" title="President of the European Commission">EC</a>)</d